platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Build up a farm & grow veggies

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Even a kid can run Dr. Pandas farm, and ours love being in charge. Who wouldnt? Milking cows, gathering honey, making jamits easy to figure out and fun selling food to unlock new activities. Plus, the papercraft-style animals couldnt be more adorable.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Grow wheat, collect milk, and make bread on your own farm.
